WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Have you ever lost your notes right before the exam or missed class and no one gives you what they covered?

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:20.500
Don't worry, because that's why I created this application. It's a web platform designed by and for students where our goal is to make life much easier.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:28.000
It's the ultimate place to upload, organize, and find all the notes you need to pass.

00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:36.500
The idea is to create a great collaborative community. Here you can find notes on absolutely everything.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:46.000
Do you need a visual summary to understand the French Revolution? We have it. Looking for biology outlines or web programming tricks?

00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:58.500
They are here too. Just use the search engine, filter by subject, and in a couple of clicks, you'll have on your screen the best materials shared by your classmates.

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:05.000
And the best part is how easy it is to do your part.

00:01:05.500 --> 00:01:15.500
Uploading your own notes takes seconds. Plus, the app is fully responsive and accessible. What does this mean?

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:25.000
Well, you can take a picture of your notebook and upload it directly from your mobile while riding the bus.

00:01:25.500 --> 00:01:35.500
The design uses clear colors and fonts so you can read for hours without straining your eyes.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:43.000
But this isn't just a drawer for PDFs, it's a community.

00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:57.000
That's why we have a chat section where you can ask questions live, debate a syllabus, or even form study groups.

00:01:57.500 --> 00:02:07.000
Ultimately, this is here so we can all help each other.

00:02:07.500 --> 00:02:23.000
Join, share your knowledge, find what you're missing, and go for that A+. See you inside.